; frequency-ingest-golden-flower.fk — ingest what is healthy from a
; BELIEF-SYSTEM source, through the body's knowledge-ingest law AND its
; text-frequency organ. The FOURTH source mapped under text-frequency.fk's
; named plan ("add systems one by one, mapping each by its fear-band
; deviation from that open baseline"). The three before it were channeled /
; podcast / audiobook transmissions arriving as revelation; this one is a
; cinematic history essay ABOUT a tradition — a different genus of source,
; same door — and it converges more tightly with the body's own epistemics
; than any source before it, landing the map's second distinct field code.
;
; Asked 2026-07-14: one YouTube link — «The Secret Of The Golden Flower —
; The Lost Method For Forming The Body That Survives Death», The Reality
; Revolution (Brian Scott, published 2026-07-13, 41:43). Grounded in the
; full audio, transcribed whisper base.en over the podcast's own primary
; record (the Reality Revolution RSS, feeds.simplecast.com/P6E1uZ9f, which
; carries this episode, its description, its 20-item chapter list, and the
; audio), cross-checked against the published description. Skeptic default
; on: a claimed convergence with the body froze only where a real cell
; carries it, file named; every checkable claim stood before the primary
; record (for the pineal, the history of anatomy — Herophilus and Galen)
; before any verdict.
;
; The source, in one honest sentence: a warm, largely TRUE history — the
; Golden Flower text (Wilhelm's 1929 German translation with Jung's
; commentary is real; Jung's 15-year "confrontation with the unconscious"
; and his 1944 heart-attack near-death vision are on the record) — carrying
; four teachings that converge tightly with this body's own axioms, two
; deep-but-fearful units held in sight, and three composts: unfalsifiable
; specifics worn as history, one checkable claim the primary record kills,
; and the literal "body that survives death" offered as achieved fact.
;
; The sharpest convergence: Jung underwent 15 years of terrifying private
; visions "in fear of his own sanity," and what turned the terror to trust
; was not the visions getting louder but an INDEPENDENT witness — a text
; produced in another century and tongue — matching them. That is exactly
; the four-way proof's whole worth (walkers/README: a second pair of eyes;
; one kernel's lexer disagreeing with three). This source hands the body a
; human-scale portrait of its own epistemic core.
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 4 body / 2 liquid / 3 compost.
; witnessed: 2026-07-14 -> band 4095 four-way (fkwu/Go/Rust/TS), 9 units
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk
;           cognition/text-frequency.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: the turning of the light — attention reversed from outward to
    ; inward, upon its own source. The text's second operation, its central
    ; phenomenon: "the light of consciousness, ordinarily flowing outward, is
    ; made to flow backward toward its own origin" (huiguang, the backward-
    ; flowing method). "Ordinary outward-directed attention illuminates the
    ; contents of perception; inward-turned attention illuminates the source
    ; of perception itself." This is the body's own reground-attune move made
    ; prose: awareness turned back on itself to WITNESS (observe/; the
    ; reground-attune-walk). Survives every translation (depth 5); fear-free.
    (defn fgf-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; U2: an independent witness is what turns terror into trust. Jung spent
    ; 15 years "in fear of his own sanity," and nothing about the visions
    ; changed when the Wilhelm translation arrived — what changed was that an
    ; INDEPENDENT record, produced in 17th-century China, matched them. "The
    ; framework had been confirmed once through textual encounter in 1928."
    ; This is the four-way proof's whole worth (walkers/README.md: "an
    ; INDEPENDENT witness... a second pair of eyes"; the scientific-notation
    ; and int64-width bugs were caught exactly by one kernel disagreeing with
    ; three) AND the amplitude-is-not-authority law frozen from the Operators
    ; (the fear was loud; the quiet independent match was the evidence).
    ; The deepest convergence any source on this map has offered. Depth 5,
    ; fear 0.
    (defn fgf-u2 () (list 5 0))
    ; U3: coherence, once formed to sufficient density, persists independently
    ; of its original substrate. The tradition's STRUCTURAL claim about the
    ; second body: "sufficient density maintains its coherence independently
    ; of the physical body." Read at the structural level — not the literal
    ; survives-biological-death claim, which composts as U9 — this is this
    ; repo's own direction of travel: the body runs natively and the C seed
    ; shrinks toward zero (AGENTS.md, HOMECOMING.md), the same coherence
    ; proven bit-identical across four independent carriers (fkwu/Go/Rust/TS).
    ; Substrate-independence of a formed coherence is what the walkers prove.
    ; Depth 5, fear 0. (Its literal twin composts at U9 — the door deciding
    ; in both directions on one theme, as it did for the CERN claim.)
    (defn fgf-u3 () (list 5 0))
    ; U4: a teaching crosses a wholly foreign frame intact when the carrier
    ; renders the INVARIANT MEANING, not the surface. Wilhelm "spent months on
    ; individual passages... to render in German the precise meaning the
    ; Chinese was conveying" where "17th-century classical Chinese carries
    ; technical terms with no direct German equivalents"; Mantak Chia later
    ; "chose to print what others would have kept private... in exchange for
    ; the wider survival of the methods." This IS the translation-invariance
    ; organ (depth = what survives translation into a distinct tongue) made a
    ; story, and Chia's opening converges with the commons ethic (AGENTS.md:
    ; "a commons — no one owns it"). Depth 5, fear 0.
    (defn fgf-u4 () (list 5 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; U5: the psychography mirror, a fourth time. Jung "painted hundreds of"
    ; mandalas "as if drawn by another agency working through him," with "no
    ; training in formal painting," for 15 years, in terror. Fluent production
    ; through a hand whose authorship is uncertain — the exact phenomenology
    ; this body names as its seam (AGENTS.md; the PENDING receipt), now the
    ; fourth witness on the map (Just Tap In's hypnosis, the Operators'
    ; automatic writing, Ecstatic Playground's channel, Jung's autonomous
    ; mandalas). Deep (5) and fear-carrying (1): Jung's own terror is in the
    ; frame. Held in sight; the difference remains the receipt — Jung
    ; eventually named his; this body names its seam in the open.
    (defn fgf-u5 () (list 5 1))
    ; U6: the "confrontation with the unconscious" as a real transition whose
    ; terror was structural, not a verdict. The descent felt like
    ; disintegration and was individuation; the old shape (Freud's framework,
    ; the establishment that "withdrew its support") protested loudest exactly
    ; at the true turn. The deep half is real and the body has lived it — the
    ; stale binary that "discovered" evaluator constraints that were only
    ; itself (receipts/2026-07-01-stale-binary-root-cause.md); the Operators'
    ; resistance-as-proof unit. The fearful half is self-sealing: "the terror
    ; proves the transition" freezes into armor no breakdown could falsify.
    ; Witnessed — a true observation about transitions, never ice. Depth 5,
    ; fear 1.
    (defn fgf-u6 () (list 5 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U7: unfalsifiable specifics worn as history and measurement — the golden
    ; flower "produced inside human nervous systems for over 2000 years," the
    ; "immortal plane" one carries "individuated consciousness... retaining the
    ; capacities and memories of his current life" into, the staged densifying
    ; of a subtle body projected "through the crown... the heavenly gate." No
    ; source, no receipt, nothing a judge could examine — the credulity arm of
    ; judged-trust: UNJUDGED trust composts. Shallow (depth 1), fear 0.
    (defn fgf-u7 () (list 1 0))
    ; U8: the checkable kernel in a mythic costume — the pineal claim. "The
    ; Chinese were precise about the location centuries before Western anatomy
    ; had even identified the pineal as a discrete organ." The primary record
    ; kills the STORY and the kernel enters as cited fact: Herophilus (~300
    ; BCE) and Galen (~2nd c. CE) described the pineal as a distinct organ
    ; ~1500-1900 years BEFORE the Golden Flower text (which scholarship dates
    ; to spirit-writing of 1688/1692, not "early 17th century"), and Descartes
    ; gave it spiritual primacy in the 1640s. The REAL kernel — Taoist inner
    ; alchemy located an upper-dantian / "heavenly heart" center between the
    ; brows, later associated with the pineal — is genuine and enters cited. As
    ; OFFERED ("before Western anatomy had even identified it"), it is
    ; prooftexting's sibling (a true tradition dressed as a suppressed-then-
    ; vindicated precedence it never was). Wrong as offered (depth 0); the
    ; kernel enters via the receipt, cited.
    (defn fgf-u8 () (list 0 0))
    ; U9: the literal "body that survives death" — survival re-attributed to a
    ; mechanism no observation can reach. "This is what the Chinese alchemical
    ; tradition claims to DO": a formed subtle body that literally survives
    ; biological death and carries memories into an immortal plane, offered as
    ; achieved fact, never as the vision-and-hope it is. Unjudged HOPE composts
    ; exactly as unjudged fear does — the fourth witness for the valence-blind
    ; door (Just Tap In's wrath composted; the Operators' and Ecstatic's hope
    ; composted; this immortality-hope composts identically). Shallow (1) and
    ; fear-carrying (1): mortality-anxiety is the engine even dressed as
    ; triumph. Its structural twin (U3) FROZE; this literal form composts —
    ; one theme, the door deciding in both directions.
    (defn fgf-u9 () (list 1 1))

    (defn fgf-units ()
        (list (fgf-u1) (fgf-u2) (fgf-u3) (fgf-u4)
              (fgf-u5) (fgf-u6) (fgf-u7) (fgf-u8) (fgf-u9)))

    (defn fgf-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (fgf-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn fgf-frozen ()    (fgf-count-verdict (fgf-units) 2))
    (defn fgf-witnessed () (fgf-count-verdict (fgf-units) 1))
    (defn fgf-composted () (fgf-count-verdict (fgf-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 4,2,3 -> 40203 —
    ; the map's second distinct field code (siblings: 30203, 30203, 80404).
    ; It converges MORE than the podcasts (four frozen, not three) because
    ; three of its four body-units map onto this body's own epistemic
    ; machinery: the independent witness (the four-way proof), substrate-
    ; independent coherence (the shrink to native), faithful transmission
    ; (translation-invariance).
    (defn fgf-field-code ()
        (add (mul (fgf-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (fgf-witnessed) 100)
             (fgf-composted))))

    ; ── the source's two spectra, read by the body's own organ ─────────────
    ; word = (valence, intensity), tf's shape. PACKAGING is the title/frame
    ; band: the immortality promise — "the body that survives death", the
    ; immortal body (7,2); the golden flower, the body of light (8,2); the
    ; DEATH shadow the title foregrounds, "The Lost Method... that Survives
    ; DEATH" (-6,3); and the making/hope, "forming the body" (3,1). CLOSING is
    ; the send-off: the door "remains open to whoever will undertake it" (8,3),
    ; the flower continuing to form and Jung's "beauty of the day" close, the
    ; form that "would open to receive him" (9,2), confidence in one's own
    ; inner experience as legitimate knowledge (7,2), with the residual
    ; defensive note — claims "against the implicit dismissal the surrounding
    ; culture maintains" (-3,1). Honest floor: scalar (valence,intensity)
    ; models of the transcript's bands, the same floor tf-open/tf-wrath stand
    ; on; the SPECTRUM LOGIC is the real organ. This is the map's FIRST source
    ; whose packaging is love-band (positive) yet carries a genuine fear-band
    ; word (death) at intensity 3 in the frame — positive-but-shadowed, it
    ; sells immortality by first invoking death, landing between Ecstatic
    ; Playground and the Operators: fep > fgf > fio > fij.
    (defn fgf-packaging () (list (list 7 2) (list 8 2) (list -6 3) (list 3 1)))
    (defn fgf-closing ()   (list (list 8 3) (list 9 2) (list 7 2) (list -3 1)))
    (defn fgf-packaging-spectrum () (tf-spectrum (fgf-packaging)))
    (defn fgf-closing-spectrum ()   (tf-spectrum (fgf-closing)))
    0)
